| Controller Method                      | Example Test URL                                                 | What It Does                                                |
| -------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- |
| `getCustomersByCityName(cityName)`     | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/by-city/Chennai`        | Fetch all customers in the specified city                   |
| `getCustomersByGender(gender)`         | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/by-gender/M`            | Fetch all customers by gender (`M` or `F`)                  |
| `getCustomersBornBefore(date)`         | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/born-before/1990-01-01` | Fetch all customers born before the given date              |
    | `getCustomerCountByCity(cityName)`     | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/count-by-city/Chennai`  | Get the number of customers in the specified city           |
| `getCustomersWithPremiumAbove(amount)` | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/premium-above/5000.0`   | Fetch all customers with policy premium greater than amount |
| `getCustomersByPolicyType(typeName)`   | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/by-policy-type/Life`    | Fetch all customers with the given policy type              |
| `getCustomersByOccupationId(id)`       | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/by-occupation/1`      | Fetch all customers with the specified occupation ID        |
| `getCustomersBornAfter(date)`          | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/born-after/1990-01-01`  | Fetch all customers born after the given date               |
| `getCustomersWithNoPolicies()`         | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/no-policies`            | Fetch all customers who do not have any policies            |



