Entity: Policy

| Controller Method                     | Example Test URL                                                                 | What It Does                                                  |
| ------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `getPoliciesByPremium(amount)`        | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/by-premium/3000`                         | Fetch policies where premium is greater than the given amount |
| `getPoliciesByDateRange(start, end)`  | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/by-date?start=2023-01-01&end=2023-12-31` | Fetch policies created within a date range                    |
| `getPoliciesByCustomerName(name)`     | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/by-customer-name/John`                   | Fetch policies by customer name (partial match allowed)       |
| `getPoliciesByCustomerGender(gender)` | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/by-customer-gender/M`                    | Fetch policies for male/female customers (M or F)             |
| `getPoliciesByCustomerCity(city)`     | `GET http://localhost:8080/api/policies/by-customer-city/Chennai`                | Fetch policies where customer is from a particular city       |


